svg.text: Ask your classmates about their siblings. Use the questions below as a starting
point. Does anyone have all four kinds of sibling?
Now that you know who has brothers and sisters, you can find out who has the
most brothers and sisters! Ask your classmates how many of each kind of sibling they have.
